text: The markdown editor in the Execute details sidebar is not styled correctly, the text is too low contrast to be readable

proposedTasks.title: Fix markdown text contrast in Execute task detail sidebar
proposedTasks.description: The markdown content rendered in the Execute phase task detail sidebar has insufficient text contrast, making it unreadable. Audit all markdown rendering styles (prose text, code blocks, headings, links, list items) in the detail sidebar component and ensure they meet WCAG AA contrast ratios (4.5:1 for normal text, 3:1 for large text) in both light and dark themes. Acceptance criteria: (1) All markdown text in the Execute detail sidebar is clearly readable against its background in both light and dark themes. (2) Contrast ratios meet WCAG AA minimums. (3) Styling is consistent with markdown rendering in other parts of the app (e.g., Plan markdown view, PRD display).

taskTitles: Fix markdown text contrast in Execute task detail sidebar
